+        // written by the game and would otherwise accumulate stale framebuffer
+        // content across frames. Clear those two wing rects here, before the
+        // scene draws, so 3D geometry (whose projection IS widened by the
+        // aspect-ratio scale) redraws fresh into the wings while 2D stays put.
+        // See PHASE6_NOTES_b.md. Gated by enhancementConfig.rect.clearWings.
+        // Mischief Makers host hook. Rotating-camera scenes require a fresh
+        // HD color canvas or old sprite pixels form long trails.
